Text: Re lunch tomorrow Cc Charlespst Oops I just sent a similar email before reading this one Eric Schneider Enron Broadband Services Vance nronXgate AM To V Charles nronXgate cc Eric SchneiderEnron nron Communications Subject lunch tomorrow CharlieWould it be possible to reschedule our lunch for sometime next week say Tuesday I guess the rest of the guys had planned a lunch on Friday with additional UT alumniEnron employees You are welcome to join us however I know you said you would prefer a smaller group I definitely want to visit with you about your experiences here at Enron Just let me know what works ThanksVance

LunchCharlespst Charlie I spoke with Vance Holtzman yesterday about the of us getting together for lunch However Friday does not work because we are meeting up with a large group of interns for lunch on Friday Is it possible that we meet for lunch next Tuesday June Please let me know if this fits your schedule Thanks Eric Schneider Enron Broadband Services

Re FW Lunch Cc Charlespst Charlie Wed is supposed to be an intern lunch though the email has not yet been sent I helped EBS put together the presentation Thursday is a brown bag luncheon Can we plan on Friday Early or late Vance and I will work around your schedule Eric Schneider Enron Broadband Services V Charles nronXgate AM To Vance nronXgate Eric SchneiderEnron nron Communications cc Subject FW Lunch Cant do lunch on Tuesday due to a meeting that just got planned Lets shoot for Wed Original Message From Weldon V Charles Sent Thursday May PM To Schneider Eric Holtzman Vance Subject RE Lunch Lets shoot for lunch next Tuesday Would one of you please contact me that am to see how the day is going Its been pretty hectic lately but I think we will be able to do it Thanks Charlie Original Message From Schneider Eric Sent Thursday May AM To Weldon V Charles Holtzman Vance Subject Lunch Charlie I spoke with Vance Holtzman yesterday about the of us getting together for lunch However Friday does not work because we are meeting up with a large group of interns for lunch on Friday Is it possible that we meet for lunch next Tuesday June Please let me know if this fits your schedule Thanks Eric Schneider Enron Broadband Services
